# SparkStudio Serverless Containers — CI repo
# Only the serverless Dockerfiles and CI workflow are tracked.
# The full SparkStudio app runs locally from ~/SparkStudio-novita.

# Ignore everything by default
/*

# Allow only what CI needs
!/.github/
!.github/
!.github/**
!.gitignore
!README_SERVERLESS.md
!serverless/
!serverless/**

# Ignore macOS clutter
.DS_Store
